<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ComfortGuard HVAC Membership</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="ComfortGuard HVAC Membership - preventative maintenance plan with bi-annual tune-ups, priority scheduling, repair discounts, and stackable referral rewards."
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0b1220;
      --panel: #131c31;
      --panel-2: #1a2745;
      --text: #eaf1ff;
      --muted: #a9b6d3;
      --primary: #4da3ff;
      --primary-2: #7cc4ff;
      --accent: #67e8b5;
      --warning: #ffd166;
      --danger: #ff7a7a;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      --radius: 18px;
      --max: 1160px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(77,163,255,0.16), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #08101c 0%, #0b1220 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 30;
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      background: rgba(11,18,32,0.74);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 14px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }

    .brand-badge {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
      color: #04111f;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-2));
      color: #06111d;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(77,163,255,0.28);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-secondary {
      border-color: var(--border);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 72px 0 42px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: rgba(103,232,181,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(103,232,181,0.16);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0 0 12px; line-height: 1.1; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 4vw, 4.6rem); }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2.3vw, 2.5rem); }
    h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 62ch;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .stat, .card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .stat span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .hero-card {
      padding: 24px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -10% -30% auto;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(77,163,255,0.35), transparent 65%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .price-switch {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 18px 0 22px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .toggle {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .toggle.active {
      background: rgba(77,163,255,0.14);
      color: var(--text);
      border-color: rgba(77,163,255,0.35);
    }

    .price-value {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      margin: 6px 0;
    }

    .price-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .mini-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .mini-list li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .mini-list li::before {
      content: "✓";
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 42px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .section-head p {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 66ch;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--primary-2);
      background: rgba(77,163,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(77,163,255,0.18);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .pricing-card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .pricing-card.featured {
      border-color: rgba(103,232,181,0.35);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(103,232,181,0.08);
    }

    .badge {
      position: absolute;
      right: 18px;
      top: 18px;
      background: rgba(103,232,181,0.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(103,232,181,0.28);
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .pricing-amount {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin: 6px 0;
    }

    .pricing-sub {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .checklist {
      columns: 2;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .checklist li {
      break-inside: avoid;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .checklist li span {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .calculator-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .field {
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .field label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .field input[type="range"] {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .field input[type="number"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #0d1527;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .calc-output {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .metric {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .metric .label {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .metric .value {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .value.good { color: var(--accent); }
    .value.warn { color: var(--warning); }
    .value.bad { color: var(--danger); }

    .bar-wrap {
      width: 100%;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .bar {
      height: 100%;
      width: 0%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--primary));
      transition: width 0.25s ease;
    }

    details {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      padding: 16px 18px;
    }

    details + details {
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    details p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 12px 0 0;
    }

    .cta {
      padding: 32px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 36px 0 52px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer-box {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 18px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .grid-3,
      .grid-2,
      .calculator-grid,
      .cta {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .checklist {
        columns: 1;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .calc-output {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .container {
        width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 20px));
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 44px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#top">
        <span class="brand-badge">CG</span>
        <span>ComfortGuard HVAC Membership</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="#checklist">Checklist</a>
        <a href="#referrals">Referrals</a>
        <a href="#profit">Profitability</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#join">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="hero" id="top">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Preventative maintenance + stackable referral rewards</div>
        <h1>Protect home comfort. Reward loyal customers. Grow recurring revenue.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          ComfortGuard is a simple residential HVAC maintenance membership with
          two professional tune-ups per year, priority scheduling, repair savings,
          and a referral system that lets customers save up to 50% at renewal.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#pricing">View Membership</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#referrals">Try Referral Calculator</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <strong>2 visits/year</strong>
            <span>Spring AC tune-up + Fall heating tune-up</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <strong>Up to 50% off</strong>
            <span>Stackable referral savings with a hard cap</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <strong>15% labor discount</strong>
            <span>Plus no overtime or diagnostic fees on covered repairs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card hero-card">
        <div class="tag">Membership Snapshot</div>
        <h3>One plan. Clear value.</h3>

        <div class="price-switch">
          <button class="toggle active" id="toggleMonthly" type="button">Monthly</button>
          <button class="toggle" id="toggleAnnual" type="button">Annual</button>
        </div>

        <div class="price-value" id="heroPrice">$19.99</div>
        <div class="price-note" id="heroPriceNote">per month on auto-pay</div>

        <ul class="mini-list">
          <li>Two 20-point preventative maintenance visits every year</li>
          <li>Priority scheduling when service demand is high</li>
          <li>Minor refrigerant top-offs included when needed</li>
          <li>Written service report with photos and recommendations</li>
          <li>Referral rewards tracked for renewal savings</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section id="pricing">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Simple, transparent pricing</h2>
            <p>
              Designed to be customer-friendly while keeping the contractor protected with
              realistic pricing and a discount cap.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-2">
          <div class="card pricing-card featured">
            <div class="badge">Most Flexible</div>
            <div class="tag">Auto-pay Plan</div>
            <h3>Monthly Membership</h3>
            <div class="pricing-amount">$19.99</div>
            <div class="pricing-sub">$239.88 annualized</div>
            <ul class="mini-list">
              <li>2 preventative maintenance visits per year</li>
              <li>Priority scheduling</li>
              <li>15% off repair labor</li>
              <li>No overtime or diagnostic fees on covered repairs</li>
              <li>Referral discounts applied to next billing cycle when eligible</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card pricing-card">
            <div class="tag">Best Cash Flow</div>
            <h3>Annual Prepaid</h3>
            <div class="pricing-amount">$229</div>
            <div class="pricing-sub">save about $11 vs. monthly</div>
            <ul class="mini-list">
              <li>Full year of scheduled seasonal maintenance</li>
              <li>Ideal for homeowners who want one simple annual payment</li>
              <li>Referral discounts apply at renewal</li>
              <li>Great option for loyalty and retention campaigns</li>
              <li>Clear value with no surprise tune-up charges</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="perks">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Why homeowners say yes</h2>
            <p>
              The value isn’t just maintenance. The plan combines convenience, peace of mind,
              preferred service access, and real savings when repairs happen.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="tag">Peace of Mind</div>
            <h3>Seasonal tune-ups</h3>
            <p>Keep systems running efficiently with professional spring and fall service visits.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="tag">Speed</div>
            <h3>Priority scheduling</h3>
            <p>Members move to the front of the line when same-day or next-day openings exist.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="tag">Savings</div>
            <h3>Repair discounts</h3>
            <p>Enjoy 15% off repair labor plus no overtime or diagnostic fees on covered repairs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="checklist">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Full 20-point preventative maintenance checklist</h2>
            <p>
              This checklist is performed during each maintenance visit and gives the customer
              a tangible sense of value and professionalism.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Inspect and calibrate thermostat settings<span>Confirm the system is reading and responding correctly.</span></li>
          <li>Tighten electrical connections and measure voltage/current<span>Reduce risk of failure and spot unsafe conditions early.</span></li>
          <li>Lubricate moving parts<span>Help motors and bearings run smoothly and reduce wear.</span></li>
          <li>Clean evaporator and condenser coils<span>Improve heat transfer and overall efficiency.</span></li>
          <li>Check refrigerant levels and inspect for leaks<span>Minor top-offs included when needed.</span></li>
          <li>Clean and adjust blower assembly/components<span>Support proper airflow and reduce strain.</span></li>
          <li>Inspect and test ignition system and safety controls<span>Critical for reliable heating operation.</span></li>
          <li>Check heat exchanger or air handler<span>Identify cracks, wear, and safety concerns.</span></li>
          <li>Inspect ductwork for leaks or damage<span>Catch airflow losses and comfort problems.</span></li>
          <li>Test starting capabilities and capacitors<span>Prevent no-start issues during peak season.</span></li>
          <li>Measure temperature differentials and airflow<span>Verify performance and comfort delivery.</span></li>
          <li>Inspect condensate drains and clean as needed<span>Reduce overflow and moisture issues.</span></li>
          <li>Replace standard air filter<span>Or offer upgraded filtration options.</span></li>
          <li>Check for carbon monoxide and gas leaks<span>Especially important during heating season.</span></li>
          <li>Evaluate overall system efficiency<span>Recommend practical performance improvements.</span></li>
          <li>Provide a written report with photos<span>Build trust with documented findings.</span></li>
          <li>Inspect accessible insulation and cabinet condition<span>Spot wear affecting performance.</span></li>
          <li>Check disconnects and service access condition<span>Help identify electrical safety concerns.</span></li>
          <li>Listen for unusual vibration or noise<span>Catch developing mechanical issues earlier.</span></li>
          <li>Document minor issues before they become costly<span>Supports repair upsells without pressure.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="referrals">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Refer &amp; Save calculator</h2>
            <p>
              Existing members earn 10% off their next annual bill for each successful referral,
              stacked up to a maximum of 50% off. New customer must sign up for a 12-month plan,
              complete the first visit, and remain active for 30 days to qualify.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="calculator-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="tag">Customer Savings</div>
            <h3>Referral discount calculator</h3>

            <div class="field">
              <label for="referralsRange">Number of successful referrals: <span id="referralCountLabel">0</span></label>
              <input id="referralsRange" type="range" min="0" max="10" step="1" value="0" />
            </div>

            <div class="field">
              <label for="annualPrice">Annual membership price ($)</label>
              <input id="annualPrice" type="number" min="0" step="0.01" value="229" />
            </div>

            <div class="calc-output">
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="label">Discount Rate</span>
                <span class="value" id="discountRate">0%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="label">Renewal Price</span>
                <span class="value" id="renewalPrice">$229.00</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="label">Customer Saves</span>
                <span class="value good" id="customerSavings">$0.00</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="label">Cap Status</span>
                <span class="value" id="capStatus">Below cap</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bar-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="bar" id="discountBar"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="tag">Examples</div>
            <h3>How stacking works</h3>
            <ul class="mini-list" id="exampleList">
              <li>0 referrals → $229.00</li>
              <li>1 referral → $206.10</li>
              <li>2 referrals → $183.20</li>
              <li>3 referrals → $160.30</li>
              <li>4 referrals → $137.40</li>
              <li>5+ referrals → $114.50</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="profit">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Profitability check for the contractor</h2>
            <p>
              The model stays healthy because most customers refer 0–2 people, repair work is
              high margin, and even a max-discount member can still generate strong lifetime value
              through loyalty, service calls, and future replacement opportunities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="calculator-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="tag">Business Calculator</div>
            <h3>Plan margin calculator</h3>

            <div class="field">
              <label for="deliveryCost">Estimated annual delivery cost per customer ($)</label>
              <input id="deliveryCost" type="number" min="0" step="0.01" value="115" />
            </div>

            <div class="field">
              <label for="planRevenue">Membership revenue before discount ($)</label>
              <input id="planRevenue" type="number" min="0" step="0.01" value="229" />
            </div>

            <div class="field">
              <label for="profitReferrals">Referrals earned by this customer: <span id="profitReferralsLabel">0</span></label>
              <input id="profitReferrals" type="range" min="0" max="10" step="1" value="0" />
            </div>

            <div class="calc-output">
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="label">Discounted Revenue</span>
                <span class="value" id="discountedRevenue">$229.00</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="label">Gross Profit</span>
                <span class="value good" id="grossProfit">$114.00</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="label">Gross Margin</span>
                <span class="value good" id="grossMargin">49.8%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="label">Interpretation</span>
                <span class="value" id="marginStatus">Strong positive margin</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="tag">Why It Works</div>
            <h3>Beyond the maintenance bill</h3>
            <ul class="mini-list">
              <li>Most customers stay in the 0–2 referral range, preserving strong margin.</li>
              <li>Each referral brings in a new member at full starting price.</li>
              <li>Maintenance members convert to repairs and upgrades more often.</li>
              <li>Priority service and labor discounts increase retention and trust.</li>
              <li>Referred customers are usually cheaper to acquire than paid ads.</li>
              <li>Lifetime value often matters more than the margin on one renewal bill.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Terms and FAQs</h2>
            <p>
              Clear terms protect the contractor and keep the offer easy for customers to understand.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <details open>
          <summary>When does the referral discount apply?</summary>
          <p>
            The discount applies at renewal or the next billing cycle after the referral requirements
            are met: the referred customer signs up for a 12-month plan, completes the first visit,
            and remains active for 30 days.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>Is there a limit to how much a customer can save?</summary>
          <p>
            Yes. Referral rewards stack at 10% per successful referral, capped at 50% off the bill.
            This keeps the plan generous for customers while protecting profitability.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>What happens if a membership lapses?</summary>
          <p>
            Discounts are non-transferable and expire if the membership lapses or is canceled. Auto-renew
            terms and cancellation windows should be stated clearly in the final membership agreement.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>Can pricing change over time?</summary>
          <p>
            Yes. The contractor may reserve the right to adjust pricing annually with advance notice,
            such as 60 days before renewal.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="join">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card cta">
          <div>
            <div class="tag">Launch-Ready Concept</div>
            <h2>Roll this out as a real offer</h2>
            <p>
              Pair this page with a one-page agreement PDF, a CRM-generated referral code,
              and an email/SMS campaign to existing customers. It is simple, marketable,
              and easy to explain in the field.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:flex-start;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:info@example.com?subject=ComfortGuard%20Membership%20Inquiry">Request Membership</a>
